# NOTE: chatgpt-app/public/canva-app/ used to be gitignored because it's a
# build artifact of the sibling "AI Presentation Canva Templates" Vite app.
# Vercel/GitHub Pages cannot rebuild it on their runners — it depends on
# private @canva-ct/* npm packages — so we commit the pre-built bundle
# directly. To refresh it locally:
#   cd "AI Presentation Canva Templates"
#   npx vite build --outDir ../chatgpt-app/public/canva-app
# then commit the updated files under chatgpt-app/public/canva-app/.

